wbrw9jXv_yItyYtnmFGdprDFcsM9guoIeg6XuQkW7BwAT_I8TosE2DEOkCyWwnFpq-OwbOtTE3qlU8IXY2L5PDnoxODTCv-E7AvfrMFH1YyHpcnUdVJtyqm22sGyiATbT35qpeEmqUESfKw/RgPuLECivtz48PXiIZ4denDT-2mDxVFc/9" target="_blank"&gt;在提示和加班上税的计划&lt;/a&gt;应过期。议员们还希望使特朗普2017年税收方案中设定的低收入税率永久性。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;委员会负责的联邦预算&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;分析&lt;/strong&gt;是中间派财政监管机构集团，表明将新的福利扩大了整整十年将使&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/kjnglfGj2Gt9Sq8DgvXDoAgy47rmh0E8VKDJRMr-fJ6fCRWGQgnchbvAn5H2SS9FVJXTZJMCGMKBZ5KK7mnPMkAdXTuksxZNqrH1plblMEsPvh-hQxj5lVnAhzMzvuby_pA54IDuVykSc9S8H_3fdqbV2bwxFfsIzTSa-KNpEWOqb8Mkxno3l26b0i5SASRigJYLHzrtJ2Gwcy4nrsp_qjmZPNdIlFyDdnCIubFeL3QJf3Ygb-tuPjPcFiHcVpA2zS11EQhMmayz_HXcE9Ktf0XRIg/b6CP8OJjzC-Rz4YigPUgRIgrOmlIPsVp/9" target="_blank"&gt;赤字的累积增加到5.2万亿美元&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Wj6LBDpCy-R4JSqPOnWwVZsbBgiBhWbgGhb9Y_UVs1BhDUGV1IgAN48sAZif3L6MUXg24xjlKjcKeQ1RHqCueNQxW7bU_uMdHMDALbZxHBETB1T7jY0yBDXpyBqoEzpqZKENS-RMN3XXfO-AtmEHwarlOyMj0SObpxcUARR75y4HOBFzg5Tz3YUeLSGqwjkCaWwqw_PyikQTpF3umVs2XNuQxxZSR3bucS6MCKnjR8YAhFUsCUjpgGPLIvbDFSCAqrBxUVxf4WljFVw1p-8GYN724g/9duEw8QrI6YRxiK6rI5eGcSQv_XmzExW/9" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3Ny6qIo3GbI/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="alt" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3Ny6qIo3GbI/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" width="530" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="bor